---
import Layout from "~layouts/index.astro"

import collapseWhitespace from "~utilities/collapseWhitespace"

const md = " — "

const meta = {
	description: collapseWhitespace(`
		CyberFern makes cybersecurity practical, proportionate, and human.
		We help startups, small businesses, and organisations build strong
		security foundations through consulting, training, and tailored
		programmes.
	`),
	title: "CyberFern | Cybersecurity Made Practical",
}
---

<Layout {meta}>
	<main id="main-content">
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-text">
				<header>
					<h1>
						Cybersecurity made practical,<br />proportionate, and human
					</h1>
				</header>
				<p>
					Whether you're a startup finding your feet, a small business
					protecting what you've built, or an organisation ready to level up
					your security culture{md}CyberFern can help.
				</p>
				<p>
					We bring more than twenty years of experience in software development,
					business management, and cybersecurity to every engagement. <span
						class="highlight">No jargon, no fear-mongering.</span
					>
					Just clear, honest guidance.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-image">
				<picture>
					<source
						srcset="/images/hero.avif"
						type="image/avif"
					/>
					<source
						srcset="/images/hero.webp"
						type="image/webp"
					/>
					<img
						alt="Native New Zealand fern fronds"
						height="450"
						src="/images/hero.jpg"
						width="675"
					/>
				</picture>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="what audiences">
			<header>
				<h2>Who We Help</h2>
			</header>
			<div class="card one">
				<h3><a href="/startups/">Startups</a></h3>
				<p>
					Starting up is hard enough without worrying about cybersecurity. Get a
					free consultation to understand your real risk picture from day one.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card two">
				<h3><a href="/small-businesses/">Small Businesses</a></h3>
				<p>
					Think you're too small to worry about cyber threats? That's the most
					common misconception we hear. Let us help you protect what you've
					built.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card three">
				<h3><a href="/workshops/">Workshops &amp; Training</a></h3>
				<p>
					Six focused workshops that bridge the gap between technical security
					and business thinking{md}from quantifying cyber risk to boardroom
					presentations.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card four">
				<h3><a href="/champions/">Security Champions</a></h3>
				<p>
					A structured programme to embed security into your software
					development lifecycle{md}faster, more secure delivery without burning
					people out.
				</p>
			</div>
			<p class="lets-talk">
				<a
					class="button"
					href="https://calendly.com/admin-cyberfern/free-consultation-with-cyberfern"
					rel="external"
					>BOOK A FREE CONSULTATION</a
				>
			</p>
		</section>
		<section class="section-shaded">
			<header>
				<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
			</header>
			<div>
				<p>
					Like the native ferns of New Zealand, we believe in supporting growth
					from the ground up. We're passionate about <strong
						>helping organisations build strong security foundations{
							md
						}with</strong
					> practical, proportionate solutions focused on what matters most.
				</p>
				<p>
					What makes us different is our <strong>holistic vision</strong> of cybersecurity.
					We know that effective security isn't just about technology{md}it's
					about how your people work, how your processes flow, and how your
					business grows. By
					<strong>integrating</strong> all these elements, we create solutions that
					truly fit your organisation's reality and support your journey.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="section-light">
			<header>
				<h2>Testimonials</h2>
			</header>
			<div>
				<blockquote>
					<p>
						"Anna has been fantastic in our Cyber Security Journey. Helping us
						with processes and overall mindset to keep PAM safe within our
						acceptable risk appetite.
					</p>
					<p>
						"She has opened our eyes to risks we never even considered and
						reassured us on areas that need less attention at this stage."
					</p>
					<footer>
						<cite>
							<a
								href="https://mypam.nz"
								rel="external"
							>
								<picture>
									<source
										srcset="/images/pam.avif"
										type="image/avif"
									/>
									<source
										srcset="/images/pam.webp"
										type="image/webp"
									/>
									<img
										alt="PAM — Helping busy families thrive"
										height="105"
										src="/images/pam.png"
										width="180"
									/>
								</picture>
							</a>
						</cite>
					</footer>
				</blockquote>
				<blockquote>
					<p>
						"We engaged Cyberfern to conduct a security review of our system,
						and the experience exceeded our expectations. From the outset, they
						demonstrated a deep understanding of cybersecurity best practices
						and took the time to understand our specific challenges and business
						needs.
					</p>
					<p>
						"Their thorough assessment identified key areas for improvement
						while also highlighting our existing strengths. What truly stood out
						was their ability to explain complex security concepts in a clear
						and actionable way, making it easy for our team to implement the
						recommended changes.
					</p>
					<p>
						"Anna was professional, detail-oriented, and proactive throughout
						the process. Her insights have significantly strengthened our
						security posture, and we feel much more confident in our system's
						resilience.
					</p>
					<p>
						"We highly recommend Cyberfern to any organisation looking for
						expert security consulting."
					</p>
					<footer>
						<cite>
							<a
								href="https://ezidocs.com/"
								rel="external"
							>
								<picture>
									<source
										srcset="/images/ezidocs.avif"
										type="image/avif"
									/>
									<source
										srcset="/images/ezidocs.webp"
										type="image/webp"
									/>
									<img
										alt="Ezidocs"
										height="31"
										src="/images/ezidocs.png"
										width="180"
									/>
								</picture>
							</a>
						</cite>
					</footer>
				</blockquote>
				<p class="lets-talk">
					<a
						class="button"
						href="mailto:info@cyberfern.com"
						>GET IN TOUCH</a
					>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<aside
		id="about"
		class="about"
	>
		<header>
			<h2>About CyberFern</h2>
		</header>
		<div class="about-content">
			<p>CyberFern was founded by Anna Lezhikova.</p>
			<p>
				She has more than twenty years of experience in communications, business
				management, software development, DevOps, and DevSecOps. She understands
				not only the technology, but also people and processes: the triad of
				good cybersecurity.
			</p>
			<p>
				Let&rsquo;s work together to protect what matters most to you and your
				organisation.
			</p>
		</div>
	</aside>
</Layout>
